{"tid":1228380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】坂本龍一為港人打氣：香港加油！","createTime":"2019-06-15T16:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T17:29:45.000Z","uid":120399,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6724b817f1babf0d39010e2f48e383fb6b02d263","tid":1228380,"uid":120399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:57:29.000Z","msg":"政府強推《逃犯條例》修訂引發反送中運動，獲得國際社會的關注。本地著名音樂家龔志成今日在 FB 發文，表示收到日本音樂大師坂本龍一的短訊，坂本龍一在短訊中為香港人加油打氣。<br />\n龔志成在 FB 引述坂本龍一的短訊寫道：「hi friends, i send you guys and the HK people '香港加油!'.」<br />\n資深音樂人黃志淙亦收到坂本龍一相同的短訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E5%9D%82%E6%9C%AC%E9%BE%8D%E4%B8%80%E7%82%BA%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%93%E6%B0%A3-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8A%A0%E6%B2%B9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E5%259D%2582%25E6%259C%25AC%25E9%25BE%258D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%25B0%25A3-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%25B2%25B9%2F&d=YAxVOUHAW5%2FtYfR1oVoe24TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=3eaeca0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E5%259D%2582%25E6%259C%25AC%25E9%25BE%258D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%25B0%25A3-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%25B2%25B9%2F&h=163451b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E5%9D%82%E6%9C%AC%E9%BE%8D%E4%B8%80%E7%82%BA%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%93%E6%B0%A3-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8A%A0%E6%B2%B9/</a>"},{"pid":"37fe0ec6459a7266d192adf0f84feeaec5c9440e","tid":1228380,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:04:58.000Z","msg":"Connect埋日本<img src=\"/assets/face